### Hotel Guest Review System - API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@token = 

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### API Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/status

### Login as Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@grandhotel.ru",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Login as Manager
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "manager@grandhotel.ru",
  "password": "manager123"
}

### Register New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "test123",
  "first_name": "Test",
  "last_name": "User",
  "role": "manager"
}

### Create Booking (with automatic risk check)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hotel_id": "YOUR_HOTEL_ID",
  "source": "booking.com",
  "booking_external_id": "BK123456",
  "guest_first_name": "Иван",
  "guest_last_name": "Иванов",
  "guest_phone": "+79161234567",
  "guest_email": "ivan@example.com",
  "checkin_date": "2026-04-01",
  "checkout_date": "2026-04-05",
  "room_type": "Standard",
  "total_amount": 15000,
  "currency": "RUB"
}

### Get Booking Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/BOOKING_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List All Bookings
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/?skip=0&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Guest Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/guests/GUEST_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List All Guests
GET {{baseUrl}}/guests/?skip=0&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Review for Guest
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_id": "BOOKING_ID",
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "Хороший гость, все в порядке",
  "tags": [],
  "damage_amount": null,
  "unpaid_amount": null
}

### Create Negative Review
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_id": "BOOKING_ID",
  "rating": 2,
  "comment": "Повреждение мебели, шумное поведение",
  "tags": ["property_damage", "noise"],
  "damage_amount": 5000,
  "unpaid_amount": null
}

### Get Guest Reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews/guest/GUEST_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
